ovpn_file.file:
client
dev tun
proto tcp
remote 34.87.187.71 1194
http-proxy 34.87.187.71 8080
http-proxy-retry
http-proxy-timeout 5
http-proxy-option CUSTOM-HEADER CONNECT HTTP/1.1
http-proxy-option CUSTOM-HEADER Host api.twitter.com
http-proxy-option CUSTOM-HEADER X-Online-Host api.twitter.com
http-proxy-option CUSTOM-HEADER X-Forwarded-For api.twitter.com
http-proxy-option CUSTOM-HEADER Connection: X-Forward-Host
http-proxy-option CUSTOM-HEADER Connection: X-Online-Host
http-proxy-option CUSTOM-HEADER Connection: Keep-Alive
http-proxy-option CUSTOM-HEADER Connection: Dual-Connection
persist-key
persist-tun
pull
setenv FRIENDLY_NAME

resolv-retry infinite
nobind
user nobody
comp-lzo
remote-cert-tls server
verb 3
mute 2
connect-retry 5 5
connect-retry-max 8080
mute-replay-warnings
redirect-gateway def1
script-security 2
auth-user-pass
cipher none
auth none
